# {{ report.title }}

## Overview

### About C4

Code4rena (C4) is an open organization consisting of security researchers,
auditors, developers, and individuals with domain expertise in smart
contracts.

A C4 audit is an event in which community participants, referred to as
Wardens, review, audit, or analyze smart contract logic in exchange for
a bounty provided by sponsoring projects.

During the audit outlined in this document, C4 conducted an analysis of
{{ report.sponsor }}'s smart contracts. The audit took place from
{{ report.start_date }} to {{ report.end_date }}.

